  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13090992/snowy-trees-838x280.jpg" alt="December ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/e32e4b882db446a4a9decdbd856a2bc4" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Downhill in December - Book your December ski holiday today and experience the most wonderful time of the year on the slopes. Experience a traditional Christmas whilst exploring festive markets or<span> </span><span>ring in the New Year on skis with spectacular firework displays.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="#destinations" data-anchor="#destinations">Ski Holiday Destinations</a> | <a href="#lapland" data-anchor="#lapland">Lapland Holidays</a> | <a href="#accommodation" data-anchor="#accommodation">The Best Accommodation</a></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December" class="c-btn">View December ski deals</a><a data-udi="umb://document/a2fdb805021d4e06a9f4347cf475473c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a2fdb805021d4e06a9f4347cf475473c}" title="Best Ski Package Holiday Deals"></a></p>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<p><img src="/media/13090993/christmas-trees-lights-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9770efdc5def423ba0d5914a4012148a" /></p>
<h3>Christmas 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Choose a December ski holiday and experience the magic of Christmas. With snow-covered slopes, roaring log fires and gorgeous views, December ski holidays bring you everything you need for a magical time on and off the slopes. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d}" title="Christmas Ski Holidays" class="c-btn">View Christmas ski holidays</a></div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<p><img src="/media/13090994/ski-resort-fireworks-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6f772af0e7124a64a19f1b84027be813" /></p>
<h3>New Year 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Enjoy New Year's Eve on the slopes and welcome in 2025 on a fresh set of snowy slopes. There's not much to compare to the buzz of skiing on New Year's Day and celebrating New Year's Eve in the mountains – it's a one-of-a-kind experience.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36}" title="New Year Ski Holidays" class="c-btn">View New Year ski holidays</a></div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<p><img src="/media/13090995/tignes-snow-view-of-town-314x194.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7222d2281ce34fbd925b8775565e7278" /></p>
<h3>All December 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Make your December holiday plans now. With no crowds and snow-heavy slopes, a December ski holiday is the ideal time to hit the powder. You can enjoy the winter wonderland of snow, glistening sunshine, and fresh mountain air. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December Ski Deals" class="c-btn">View December ski holidays</a></div>
<p> </p>
<h2 id="destinations">Our December ski holiday destinations</h2>
<p>Take advantage of pre-Christmas deals and empty slopes while avoiding the crowds of peak season with an early season ski trip. We have some great deals on selected European ski resorts available throughout December, including early December departures depending on your destination. If you are unsure of where to book this year, see the best <a data-udi="umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55}" title="Insider's Guide: Best High Altitude Ski Resorts">high altitude locations</a>.</p>
<div id="top" class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">France</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in France for December</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13090997/les-arcs-chair-lift-408x200.jpg" alt="Les Arcs December ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/98d303f1d82d4a76bd9911568bd8f311" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in France for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Courchevel </span></a>is the place to be on Christmas Eve, when the Saulire piste hosts a torchlit descent. Father Christmas visits too.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a> rings in the new year with a big countdown with drinks and a fireworks display at midnight. Its a great high-altitude resort, so lots of snow. </li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a> hosts a Christmas market, visits from Santa Claus, and a children's torchlit descent. The resort also hosts a New Year's Eve celebration with a DJ, torchlit descent, and fireworks display.</li>
</ul>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}?to={country:FR,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="France" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:FR,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">France ski holidays</a></div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Austria</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in Austria for December</strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 390px; height: 191px;" src="/media/13090998/austria-mayhrhofen-408x200.jpg?width=390&amp;height=191&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1692212a0e594e17b7ed0afa017e6031" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in Austria for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a> is a family-friendly ski resort and hosts a magical Christmas market with local foods, music and ice sculptures designed by local artists.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St Anton</a> is a great resort to visit in December, with a kids Christmas trail, crafting workshops, brass bands and a magical Christmas market. It’s also known for its legendary apres-ski scene - perfect for a New Years celebration.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a> is the place to go for an authentic Tirolean Christmas. The town lights up with festive Christmas markets, including carol singing and mulled wine.</li>
</ul>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}?to={country:AT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="Austria" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:AT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">Austria ski holidays</a></div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Switzerland</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in Switzerland for December</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13091000/grand-hotel-zermatterhof-winter-408x200.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5e45e7b27daa4432bac86cdef41bc029" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in Switzerland for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> has an excellent snow record and in December, you’ll be greeted by a warm and festive atmosphere, with the village light and organised events for the whole family to enjoy.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> resort is jam-packed full of fun winter activities, including classic tobogganing and winter walking. You’ll experience magical scenery on top of Eiger mountain which overlooks the beautiful village.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a> in December is simply magical. Experience a fairy tale winter in this picturesque resort overlooking Lauterbrunnen valley. Enjoy skiing, walking or simply take in the wonderful winter atmosphere.</li>
</ul>
<div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}?to={country:CH,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:CH,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">Switzerland ski holidays</a></div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Andorra</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in Andorra for December</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13090999/andorra-408x200.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/95bf197dc07947ffb2d00ee7187628e8" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in Andorra for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> resort welcomes in the New Year with a torch descent with the local ski and snowboard instructors. Then come midnight, the sky lights up with a spectacular fireworks display.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa</a> is a great place to ski for families. The resort welcomes Santa as he makes his way from the Granvalira Platform on a sleigh to the Pas community hall, greeting children on Christmas Eve.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal">Arinsal</a> is another great place for families to ski in December. Santa makes an appearance in his grotto and at Arinal gondola station. On New Years Eve, everyone gathers in the resort centre for a magical countdown and celebration.</li>
</ul>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}?to={country:AD,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="Andorra" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:AD,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">Andorra ski holidays</a></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Italy</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in Italy for December</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13091001/selva-408x200.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7d7c55f941cd42809fb383fc032745c1" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in Italy for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> has a lovely, festive Christmas market with enchanting wooden huts lining the street. You’ll get to enjoy tasty treats, handmade souvenirs and a mini gondola which stretches the length of the market for a bit of extra fun. </li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia’s</a> Christmas market is not to be missed, with local products and handicrafts on sale. The resort celebrates New Year with a torch light procession and firework display which is not to be missed. The town square itself is bustling on New Years Evening, with live music filling the streets.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8}" title="Courmayeur">Courmayeur</a> is a family-friendly resort and celebrates the magical festive season with a meet and greet with Santa Claus and the Marche’ Vert Noel Christmas market. The New Year is welcomed in with a night time torch procession and fire work display.</li>
</ul>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}?to={country:IT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="Italy" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:IT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">Italy ski holidays</a></div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Canada</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top ski resorts in Canada for December</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13091002/whistler-town-lights-408x200.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/18c9f75ed08a4913aed357fa0181571c" /></p>
<p>Our recommended resorts in Canada for a December ski holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> offers the perfect Christmas and New Year experience with twinkling lights, a snow-covered village, festive events, and plenty of activities to entertain the family plus lots of après fun for you and your friends. Winter is the most magical time of the year to visit this resort, with sparkling decorations lighting up the trees throughout the village.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff</a> kicks of the Christmas season with six weeks of magical festivities. Drop by the Christmas market, and walk through the Cascade of Time garden where you’ll witness a live Christmas story told by the animals and locals of Banff National Park.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise">Lake Louise</a> has a range of enchanting Christmas and New Year activities on offer. The resorts has fantastic, Christmas markets to enjoy with local food, drinks and festive stalls. Create unforgettable memories with a ski trip in the Canadian Rockies.</li>
</ul>
<div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}?to={country:IT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true" title="Canada" class="c-btn" data-anchor="?to={country:IT,resort:}&amp;when=09/12/2023&amp;nights=7&amp;from=&amp;adults=2&amp;children=&amp;childrenAges=&amp;flexibleDate=true">Canada ski holidays</a></div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
