<h2 id="accommodation">The best accommodation for a December ski holiday</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/71c9f06526254f03a4a3d53e17d19b41" href="/{localLink:umb://document/71c9f06526254f03a4a3d53e17d19b41}?accommodationNode=23059&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=CHSA&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=CHSA0114&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=A2&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=30/12/2023&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=" title="Hotel Park" data-anchor="?accommodationNode=23059&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=CHSA&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=CHSA0114&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=A2&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=30/12/2023&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=">Hotel Park - Saas Fee </a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091062/hotel-park-saas-fee-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/d00ebe8f82914fbeb6d8c195ba159930" /></p>
<p><span>A charming award-winning family-run hotel only a short walk from the Alpin Express lift. Hotel Park is a great value with comfortable rooms, good food, and a friendly atmosphere. </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
</div>
